The previous implementation is correct and successfully passes the provided test cases. To further enhance the main function, I will add 2 challenging unit tests.

### Improve
- Add 2 challenging unit tests to further validate the `pig_latin_transformer` function.

```julia
@testset "pig_latin_transformer" begin
    @test pig_latin_transformer(["hello", "world"]) == ["ellohay", "orldway"]
    @test pig_latin_transformer(["julia", "programming", "language"]) == ["uliay", "ogrammingpray", "anguagelay"]
end
```
